Malice/ Hellplague:
 
Malice heard Blacknightmare walk in.  He paniced and pushed Hellplague back and tried to set up.  He succeeded in sitting up, a look of confusion and embarressment all over his face.  He tried to explain, but ended up red faced and tougue tied.
 
Hellplague sat up with a satisfied look on her face.  She straightened up and sat up.  She took the sensor from Blacknightmare and checked it.  She pushed Malice on his back and set to work replacing the sensor.

airly2000 <airly2002@...> wrote:
BlackNightmare:

BlackNightmare arrived at that time and she looked shocke all, she

She need all her control to say that and seem calmed
